      • ROOT_REACTOR

        public static final PomType ROOT_REACTOR
        The root POM within the Maven build reactor.

      • REACTOR

        public static final PomType REACTOR
        A reactor POM within any directory other than the build reactor root.

      • PARENT

        public static final PomType PARENT
        The root parent POM within the build reactor. This normally has a parent outside of the build reactor.

      • API_PARENT

        public static final PomType API_PARENT
        The root parent POM of all API (and SPI) projects. This project differs from the root parent POM in that is normally exports all classes for public use.

      • MODEL_PARENT

        public static final PomType MODEL_PARENT
        The root parent POM of all Model projects. This project differs from the API parent POM in that it normally provides extended libraries and facilities for unit testing Entities - typically libraries required for JPA or JAXB tests.

      • WAR_PARENT

        public static final PomType WAR_PARENT
        The root parent POM of all Web Archive projects. This project differs from the API parent POM in that it normally provides extended libraries and facilities for testing WARs and web applications.

      • OTHER_PARENT

        public static final PomType OTHER_PARENT
        Any parent POM (other than already listed ones) within the reactor.
